prediction.sparql:
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?startDate WHERE {
  fb:m.093xn8 fb:tv.tv_character.appeared_in_tv_program ?appearance .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.series fb:m.03m8sg .
  ?appearance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.from ?startDate .
}
ORDER BY ?startDate
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?event ?end_date WHERE {
  fb:m.0j6tr fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?event .
  ?event fb:type.object.name ?name .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?name ) , "stanley cup" ) ) ?event fb:time.event.end_date ?end_date .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?end_date )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?championshipLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0xbm fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship rdfs:label ?championshipLabel
  FILTER ( lang( ?championshipLabel ) = 'en' ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?championshipLabel ) , "league" ) )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?condition ?conditionLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.02h3tp fb:medicine.notable_person_with_medical_condition.condition ?condition .
  ?condition rdfs:label ?conditionLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?conditionLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?wife ?wifeName WHERE {
  FILTER ( ?wife != fb:m.018fzs ) fb:m.018fzs fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?wife .
  ?wife rdfs:label ?wifeName .
  FILTER ( lang( ?wifeName ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?championship ?start_date WHERE {
  fb:m.0jm3v fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?start_date .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?start_date )
LIMIT 1
